&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Advanced Nurse Practitioner , Staplehurst Health Centre - Kent – Full Time or Part Time&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We currently have an Advanced Nurse Practitioner role available at our Staplehurst Health Centre.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Practice Profile:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are a busy, well established practice in a pleasant semi-rural village on the outskirts of Maidstone, in West Kent with easy access to the M20 and the coast. Its a wonderful place to live and we would look at support for relocation for the right candidate&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Practice is located in a purpose-built Health Centre and the clinical team consists of salaried GP’s practice nurses and HCA’s with a list size of 5,600 patients using the Vision Clinical System.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Advanced Nurse Practitioner Benefits:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Annual salary of up to £50,000 pro rata dependant on qualifications and experience.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;NEST Pension&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Full Time or part time &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;30 days annual leave + bank holidays&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;7 days study leave pro rata&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Services offered in Staplehurst are:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Diabetes type 1 and 2&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Asthma&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;COPD&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Minor Ops&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Joint Injections&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coils and Implants&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Medicals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Health Checks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Smoking Cessation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Minor injury&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Malling Health (UK) Limited&lt;/strong&gt; are a network of over 25 primary care sites across the UK, including GP Practices, Walk-In Centres, and Urgent Care Centres offering APMS contracts. Our practices provide traditional GP and nurse-led services for both registered and non-registered patients. Our philosophy is to provide a friendly, supportive place to work and to encourage innovation with the aim of delivering high quality care to our patients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please note that all posts are subject to an Enhanced Disclosure and Barring Service Check.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Please contact us now to be part of our dedicated team!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
